text: Željko Komšić (born 1964) is the President of Bosnia and Herzegovina. He began his term as president in 2013. His predecessor was Nebojša Radmanović. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the Presidency of Bosnia and Herzegovina Category:Current national leaders Category:Chairmen of the Presidency of Bosnia and Herzegovina
